301
00:48:37,314 --> 00:48:40,033
<i>Remember me, Kal-El.</i>

302
00:48:40,194 --> 00:48:42,025
<i>Remember me.</i>

303
00:48:50,554 --> 00:48:52,226
Superman's down there.

