<i>the growth of crystals.</i>

320
00:54:24,194 --> 00:54:25,513
<i>Sounds like hocus-pocus to me.</i>

321
00:54:25,674 --> 00:54:29,349
<i>Well, naturally, to the primitive mind,</i>
<i>any sufficiently advanced technology...</i>

322
00:54:29,514 --> 00:54:31,391
<i>...would be indistinguishable from magic.</i>

323
00:54:31,554 --> 00:54:34,830
